{"tid":751920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【賤狗】狗鐵收咁撚多錢 屌你老母又炒梯？","createTime":"2018-07-22T10:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T10:21:30.000Z","uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e23018eee328a7c6598b6ac46413c86deaf73c05","tid":751920,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:19:22.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】「我啱啱上完扶手電梯，背後突然傳嚟『嘭』一聲巨響，好似行雷咁。一望原來係炒梯，嚇死我喇！」讀者梁小姐前晚，於港鐵旺角站月台乘搭扶手電梯前往大堂，惟當其剛步出扶手電梯時，梯級突然爆開，最頂端有一梯級拱起，梯梳四散，露出長方形空隙。梁身後幾名途人亦受到波及，幸沒有受傷。隨後有港鐵職員到場處理事件。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人表示，前晚7時05分，旺角站車務控制中心職員發現大堂B出入口一條扶手梯的燈號亮起，顯示該扶手梯停止運作。職員趕至了解，發現該扶手梯的頂端梯級及梯梳損毀，立即將其圍封，並召承辦商派員到場維修。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180721/20456313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180721%2F20456313&d=TX7dcU1hfrmzBqCl9MW4zG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=95d71301\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180721%2F20456313&h=2a7c62e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180721/20456313</a>"},{"pid":"19d3abfbae0362091699d2f824c0393555d77258","tid":751920,"uid":125213,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/182058_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%2F182058_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=59f3496f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我哋話ok就得"},{"pid":"d2829ed37baf1d8ef36d270d0bcf053743c87d85","tid":751920,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T10:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/22/182114_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F22%